CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 15, 1954, pg. 12 reads: "Queen's Corontaion Ball - An all over view of the participants in the Teen-Queen Coronation Ball held at Ammon Center last Friday night, given by Hill City, shows "Queen" Patricia White and her ladies in waiting, their honor guards, and other contestants. Romaine Parham, last year's queen, crowned Miss White in charming ceremonies. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of "Queen" Patricia White, seated in front of group of young women gathered on stage, with group of young men wearing honor guard uniforms, standing in foreground, in Ammon Center for Teen-Queen Coronation Ball
